<p>I would add one more point to the advantage of a bandsawmill, and that is resale.  When you have finished your project you can pretty much bank on getting nearly 100% of your money back when you sell your mill,  this is even more true with the Norwood Lumberlite because you have added value to the saw with your labor in assembling it.  </p>
